column1: '''''Vinyar Tengwar''''' '''35''' is the thirty-fifth issue of ''[[Vinyar Tengwar]]'', a journal of the  [[Elvish Linguistic Fellowship]], devoted to the scholarly study of the invented languages of  [[J.R.R. Tolkien]].
** "Title page of the Atanatárion" — [[Carl F. Hostetter]].
** "Morgoth's Ring: A Linguistic Review — Part II" — Carl F. Hostetter and Patrick Wynne.
** "Transitions in Translations: German Translations vs. Tolkien's 'Guide to Names'. Part I — Names of Persons and Peoples" (column) — [[Arden R. Smith]].
